Description: Dltx ASA, formerly DLT ASA is a Norway-based technology company focusing on building and scaling infrastructure for Web3 through doing business with blockchains. The Company seeks to identify projects, teams, and companies within the decentralized economy and support open-source public distributed ledger technologies. The Companys strategy is to focus on the top tier blockchain and decentralized platforms, protocols, exchanges, and wallets. The Companys main assets are The Filecoin based datacentre File Storage Partners, portfolio of interests in businesses and assets focusing on distributed ledger technologies, and a claim for repayment of debt related to the previous business profile of the Company related to mining.
